@startuml
title 传感器自动采集模块_后台模式\n（心率 + 加速度双源并行采集，混合存储）

actor 用户
participant "HeartRateCollector" as HRCollector
participant "AccelerometerCollector" as AccCollector
participant "SensorDataRepository" as Repo
participant "Room Database" as DB

用户 -> HRCollector: 启动心率采集
activate HRCollector
HRCollector -> HRCollector: 每秒生成 RawHeartRate (模拟)
HRCollector -> Repo: insertRawData(rawHeartRate)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: 存储 RawDataEntity (type="heart_rate", dataJson)
deactivate Repo

用户 -> AccCollector: 启动加速度采集
activate AccCollector
AccCollector -> AccCollector: 每200ms生成 RawAccelerometer (模拟)
AccCollector -> Repo: insertRawData(rawAccelerometer)
activate Repo
Repo -> DB: 存储 RawDataEntity (type="accelerometer", dataJson)
deactivate Repo

note right of DB : 两种数据混合存储在同一张 raw_data 表中\n通过 type 字段区分，dataJson 存储各自 JSON
@enduml